videos.description: NC State QB Ryan Finley lobs one up for WR Kelvin Harmon, who makes a fantastic diving catch in the end zone for 14-yard TD.
videos.headline: NC State's Harmon lays out for terrific TD catch

videos.description: NC State RB Reggie Gallaspy II puts his head down and powers his way into the end zone for an 11-yard TD.
videos.headline: Gallaspy gallops in for TD

videos.description: Jakobi Meyers catches the ball along the sidelines, jukes a defender and dives into the end zone for a touchdown.
videos.headline: NC State's Meyers stretches for 24-yard TD

videos.description: NC State center Garrett Bradbury gets in on the action as he takes a hand off and increases the Wolfpack lead to 51-0.
